43:09.854 --> 43:11.155 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, certain things did happen.

43:11.255 --> 43:13.057 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Big ingenious
population
in Iran.

43:13.157 --> 43:17.495 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: Yes, exactly. And
you can get
around economic sanctions, to an
extent, although

43:17.595 --> 43:19.630 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
