36,000 Iranian
rials for $1, 36,000. And it was
much, much

43:32.577 --> 43:33.711 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
less just a few years ago.

43:33.811 --> 43:35.613 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
