43:35.713 --> 43:38.749 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: And so you have
serious problems
in the economy, and you have a
clear sense

43:38.850 --> 43:42.920 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
