43:44.822 --> 43:48.125 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: We know
there's elections
coming up at the end of next
week. And in

43:48.226 --> 43:52.864 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
