45:04.835 --> 45:07.138 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that system with all of its
checks and balances.

45:07.238 --> 45:10.808 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It would be very hard to move
Iran in any
direction but the direction it's
in now.

45:10.908 --> 45:13.744 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: All right,
Steve Inskeep
from National Public Radio,
